## Tamed

---



[Entity Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/entity_condition_types/tamed)

Checks whether a tamable entity is tamed. Will always return false if the entity is not tamable.

Type ID: `origins:tamed`




---

### Examples

```json
"condition": {
    "type": "origins:tamed"
}
```
